# Digitalized Procurement App

Transform your procurement process with our fully digitalized app, built with React Native, Node.js Express, and Socket.IO. Connect seamlessly with AWS for enhanced performance and scalability.

## Features

- **Effortless Data Submission:** Agents can easily submit procurement data through the intuitive app interface.
- **Advanced Analytics:** Managers can analyze market trends and competitor prices with detailed graphs and insightful data.
- **Collaborative Environment:** Enhance collaboration with in-app chats, fostering effective communication among team members.
- **Healthy Competition:** Foster healthy competition among agents with leaderboards, driving improved performance.
- **Streamlined Meetings and Events:** Organize and streamline meetings and events within the app for efficient communication.
- **Simplified Reimbursement:** Simplify reimbursement processes, making financial transactions smoother and more transparent.

## Technologies Used

- **Frontend:** React Native
- **Backend:** Node.js Express
- **Real-time Communication:** Socket.IO
- **Cloud Integration:** AWS (Amazon Web Services)

## Getting Started

1. **Clone the Repository:**

    ```bash
    git clone https://github.com/your-username/procurement-app.git
    cd procurement-app
    ```

2. **Install Dependencies:**

    ```bash
    # Install frontend dependencies
    cd frontend
    npm install

    # Install backend dependencies
    cd ../backend
    npm install
    ```

3. **Configure AWS Credentials:**
    - Set up your AWS credentials for seamless cloud integration.

4. **Run the App:**

    ```bash
    # Run the React Native app
    cd frontend
    npm start

    # Run the Node.js Express backend
    cd ../backend
    npm start
    ```

5. **Open the App:**
    - Open the app on your preferred emulator or physical device.

